The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the paramedic is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the lawyer is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is tennis and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Sport        | lacrosse | tennis     | biathlon   | water-polo     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
