 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the lawyer is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
